### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get Jobs from DB
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?page=1&limit=10&source=itviec

### Get Available Sources
GET {{baseUrl}}/crawl/sources

### Crawl JobGo
# @name crawlJobGo
POST {{baseUrl}}/crawl/jobgo
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://jobsgo.vn/viec-lam.html",
    "maxPages": 2,
    "fetchDetail": true,
    "saveToDb": true
}

### Crawl ITviec
# @name crawlITviec
POST {{baseUrl}}/crawl/itviec
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "maxPages": 1,
    "fetchDetail": true,
    "saveToDb": true
}

### Crawl Vieclam24h
# @name crawlVieclam24h
POST {{baseUrl}}/crawl/vieclam24h
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "maxPages": 1,
    "fetchDetail": true,
    "saveToDb": true
}
